text: The canton of La Bresse is an administrative division of the Vosges department, in northeastern France. It was created at the French canton reorganisation which came into effect in March 2015. Its seat is in La Bresse.Décret n° 2014-268 du 27 février 2014 portant délimitation des cantons dans le département des Vosges It consists of the following communes: #Basse- sur-le-Rupt #La Bresse #Cornimont #Faucompierre #La Forge #Gerbamont #Rochesson #Sapois #Saulxures-sur-Moselotte #Le Syndicat #Tendon #Thiéfosse #Le Tholy #Vagney #Ventron ==References== Category:Cantons of Vosges (department)
title: Canton of La Bresse
